Policy backed momentum for the field¶

  • Nov 15 2019: New York City green or solar roof mandate
  • Jan 1 2020: California state solar roof mandate
  • Dec 18 2022: Tokyo agrees on solar panel mandate
  • Jan 1 2023: Berlin solar rooftop mandate
  • Dec 8 2023: EU agrees on rooftop solar mandate

Not every roof is fit for solar¶

  • Local weather
  • Roof size

Part II: Rooftop size¶

How big does a roof need to be?

The average household needs a 5kW system

A 5kW system requires about $30m^2$

So a residential rooftop would need to be at least $240m^2$
